title: U.S. importers still paying Trump's illegal tariffs even after Supreme Court ruling
summary_full: Billions in U.S. cargo are still being slapped with Trump's "reciprocal" tariffs even after being struck down by the Supreme Court ruling.
summary_public: Billions in U.S. cargo are still being slapped with Trump's "reciprocal" tariffs even after being struck down by the Supreme Court ruling.
